# lightning-record-edit-form 
  
  //  important : it switch between two mode --create record and edit record 
  // as soon as we give the record ID as attributes to the record-edit-fomr 
     then all details will alredy appears in the fomr and we can edit that 
    
  mode -: if record id is present works as edit form 
          if record id not present then works as create record from 



1 base component which is used to create a new record
2 it has attributes  object-api-name : where we have to specify the Object 
3 it have onsucess property which will get executed when the record created successfully 


